      "file_path": "components/pm-subscription-handler/tests/test_aai_event_handler.py",
      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 37,
      "message": "I believe there are many redundant things here. It seems like you're setting up most of the application just to test your unit. Reminds me more of integration testing. I think it could be changed to: mocking the create_app() and aai_client, and since you're not really checking the db, just calling a method which interacts with it, it can be mocked and you would not need to set up the db at all.",
